## 动画实现的功能
activity动画
mz_activity_to_next_close_enter.xml   返回上级时新出来的Activity的进入动画
mz_activity_to_next_close_exit.xml    返回上一级时当前Activity的退出动画
mz_activity_to_next_open_enter.xml    跳转到下一个activity时,新activity的进入动画
mz_activity_to_next_open_exit.xml     跳转到下一个activity时,当前activity的退出动画


<item name="android:activityOpenEnterAnimation">@flyme:anim/mz_activity_to_next_open_enter</item>
<item name="android:activityOpenExitAnimation">@flyme:anim/mz_activity_to_next_open_exit</item>
<item name="android:activityCloseEnterAnimation">@flyme:anim/mz_activity_to_next_close_enter</item>
<item name="android:activityCloseExitAnimation">@flyme:anim/mz_activity_to_next_close_exit</item>

app切换动画
mz_app_to_next_close_enter.xml
mz_app_to_next_close_exit.xml
mz_app_to_next_open_enter.xml
mz_app_to_next_open_exit.xml




计算器动画
mz_calculator_big_to_middle.xml
mz_calculator_big_to_small.xml
mz_calculator_enter.xml
mz_calculator_exit.xml

桌面进入应用时的动画
mz_new_app_to_next_close_enter.xml

mz_new_app_to_next_close_exit.xml
mz_new_app_to_next_open_enter.xml
mz_new_app_to_next_open_exit.xml


<item name="android:taskOpenEnterAnimation">@flyme:anim/mz_new_app_to_next_open_enter</item>
